data.description: ***$7,500 TO GO TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY DOWN***Welcome to this magnificent 6-bedroom residence, perfectly situated on a corner lot in the well sought after La Jolla subdivision. Offering an impressive 3,617 square feet of luxurious living space, this exquisite home combines elegant design, spacious interiors, and a fantastic extended covered patio, creating an oasis for both relaxation and entertainment. Whether you're hosting gatherings or seeking a peaceful retreat, this property has it all. Situated on a corner lot, this property offers additional privacy and the luxury of a larger yard. The possibilities for landscaping, gardening, or even installing a pool are endless. This home is equipped with modern amenities, including central air conditioning and heating systems, energy-efficient appliances, and a dedicated laundry room. 6th Bedroom is currently being used as an office. Don't miss the opportunity to make this remarkable 6-bedroom house your own.
